ΜΝΗϹΘΩϹΙΟΙΦΙΛΟΙ<lb/>
ΠΑΥΛΟϹΚΑΙΜΑΤΡΩΝΙΑΝΟϹ
</p>
         </div>
         <div type="edition" ana="#b1" subtype="transcription" xml:id="hamm0040.transcription" corresp="#hamm0040.diplomatic #hamm0040.translation">
            <p>Μνήσθωσι οἱ φίλοι<lb/>
Παῦλος καὶ Ματρωνιανός.</p>
         </div>
         <div type="translation" ana="#b1" xml:id="hamm0040.translation" corresp="#hamm0040.diplomatic #hamm0040.transcription">
            <p>May the friends <persName xml:lang="grc " ref="persons.xml#hamm0040p01">Paul </persName> and <persName xml:lang="la " ref="persons.xml#hamm0040p02">Matronianus </persName> be remembered.</p>
         </div>
      <div type="edition" subtype="transcription_segmented"><p><w xml:id="hamm0040-1" xml:lang="grc">Μνήσθωσι</w> <w xml:id="hamm0040-2" xml:lang="grc">οἱ</w> <w xml:id="hamm0040-3" xml:lang="grc">φίλοι</w> <w xml:id="hamm0040-4" xml:lang="grc">Παῦλος</w> <w xml:id="hamm0040-5" xml:lang="grc">καὶ</w> <w xml:id="hamm0040-6" xml:lang="grc">Ματρωνιανός.</w></p>
</div>
</body>
